{"tid":774330,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工犯過咩錯","createTime":"2018-08-10T08:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T12:06:18.000Z","uid":71166,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"afab4dc2e7e30fc19eacc323736a976b3c6512fc","tid":774330,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"以前做pt親子導師<br />\n公司派我去工作教幾堂親子煮食<br />\n要入啲會員資料 將佢哋分組<br />\n已經一路入一路讀出聲<br />\n有個家長會員叫陳帶娣<br />\n我唔知發乜瘟<br />\n入做人哋叫陳帶套<br />\n到第一堂點名<br />\n我大聲叫陳帶套家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一嗌先知仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連label 都印帶套家長 帶套小朋友<br />\n我即講對唔住走跑出去問職員攞label手寫返<br />\n個家長即黑面由第一堂屌到我第六堂樣樣屌又唔合作<br />\n再投訴我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（好在我係外面公司派嚟唔係中心聘用，最終冇事）"},{"pid":"c7280860948ad6afda6c77470fb50cbc217470dc","tid":774330,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"滿腦子帶套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1755801bfb1236ca34c423854a67c52b466ef18","tid":774330,"uid":181671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"返工唔知醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c82ddecfb0c5c0885990a63629355f98e8c209","tid":774330,"uid":164778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主係咪痴撚線架"},{"pid":"241460af3adf1d286ed307e4392817eaca504511","tid":774330,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"笑撚死"},{"pid":"411a4877df4e54a47dc8e28f24a661ef16e07012","tid":774330,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"違反保密原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報左警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573207c37f732162da4fb387c6a30e63c3f87ff4","tid":774330,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"叻過個腦細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ebfef68c9785486c79b383f9dc32b7376b63b3","tid":774330,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:19:11.000Z","msg":"留名睇漏油事件"},{"pid":"bfd0513b5ff66cb19eb6904eb7ea5af822337d35","tid":774330,"uid":57153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係姓吳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48992a1fae8872d62ac8880408581cf6cf763af","tid":774330,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58d2408d7f36377f4a5f5976349bed59400d6030","tid":774330,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"晚晚 ot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a726a7a0be8f0b4f052ee068fb8bdaeb4f67b7fd","tid":774330,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:46:30.000Z","msg":"笑撚死"},{"pid":"d7844d5ce4d74762ce14ab4fc6116819c1e42146","tid":774330,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"帶套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7d0e40a529ba180909bf72df626f4939bc9236","tid":774330,"uid":116181,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"我喺一間物流公司做，負責幫貨船入油。果日有架船要出航遠行，咁我就一如往常咁打滿佢，送佢一程。過左一段時間就發現今次HiHi嘞，原來架船係用柴油嘅，點知一時錯手入左汽油。其實入錯油都冇咩，架船又唔會因為咁爆炸死人嘅；最多都係死火，啲貨就遲幾日到。不過公司就要賠錢，而我都有俾人炒嘅心理準備。我諗當時都仲心存一絲希望，希望架船聽聽話話，捱到去終站。<br />\n<br />\n不過架船真係喺太平洋島嶼擱淺左。我心諗出得嚟行，預左要還，已經準備定執包袱。果然好快就收到消息，不過炒嘅唔單止係我，而係成個部門十幾人，連上司嘅上司都俾人炒埋。點解呢？ 原來係架船上面係載住一啲化學物品，擱淺之後洩漏到成個海都係，公司要負責處理污染物，一賠賠幾億。而事件裡面最無辜嘅係附近一個水清沙幼嘅太平洋小島，因為生態災害，要即時封鎖隔離。 <br />\n<br />\n就因為遠在香港嘅我一時錯手，將一個太平洋小島毀於一旦"},{"pid":"2ae68eba717faea1235584709dcc84ab7775c492","tid":774330,"uid":193913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:16:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a584069b201a8cc1fd0ef849cd1062b6fe6de1f","tid":774330,"uid":21488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a7d0e40a529ba180909bf72df626f4939bc9236","tid":774330,"uid":116181,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"我喺一間物流公司做，負責幫貨船入油。果日有架船要出航遠行，咁我就一如往常咁打滿佢，送佢一程。過左一段時間就發現今次HiHi嘞，原來架船係用柴油嘅，點知一時錯手入左汽油。其實入錯油都冇咩，架船又唔會因為咁爆炸死人嘅；最多都係死火，啲貨就遲幾日到。不過公司就要賠錢，而我都有俾人炒嘅心理準備。我諗當時都仲心存一絲希望，希望架船聽聽話話，捱到去終站。<br />\n<br />\n不過架船真係喺太平洋島嶼擱淺左。我心諗出得嚟行，預左要還，已經準備定執包袱。果然好快就收到消息，不過炒嘅唔單止係我，而係成個部門十幾人，連上司嘅上司都俾人炒埋。點解呢？ 原來係架船上面係載住一啲化學物品，擱淺之後洩漏到成個海都係，公司要負責處理污染物，一賠賠幾億。而事件裡面最無辜嘅係附近一個水清沙幼嘅太平洋小島，因為生態災害，要即時封鎖隔離。 <br />\n<br />\n就因為遠在香港嘅我一時錯手，將一個太平洋小島毀於一旦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"其實點解呢單野會有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"75ce29d283a2b7dcf1854155ef4adac8e6424b0b","tid":774330,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}